  "body": "It is currently possible to do this:\n\n```\npragma solidity ^0.4.3;\n\ncontract Constants {\n\n    uint constant FLAG = 0x1;\n}\n\ncontract Test is Constants {\n\n    function x() returns (uint) {\n        return Constants.FLAG;\n    }\n}\n```\n\nBut surely it should be possible to do this:\n\n```\npragma solidity ^0.4.3;\n\ncontract Constants {\n\n    uint constant FLAG = 0x1;\n}\n\ncontract Test {\n\n    function x() returns (uint) {\n        return Constants.FLAG;\n    }\n}\n```\n",
